msgid "The Antigravity Standard"
msgstr "Antigravity Standarti"

msgid "Pure Mastery."
msgstr "Sof Mahorat."

msgid "Tonsor is an exclusive digital ecosystem for the world's most elite barbers and discerning clients. Experience precision grooming through an uncompromising lens."
msgstr "Tonsor - dunyodagi eng elita sartaroshlar va nozik mijozlar uchun eksklyuziv raqamli ekotizim. Murosasiz nigoh orqali aniq parvarishni his qiling."

msgid "Start Experience"
msgstr "Tajribani Boshlash"

msgid "Master Barbers"
msgstr "Usta Sartaroshlar"

msgid "Monthly Sessions"
msgstr "Oylik Seanslar"

msgid "Precision Rate"
msgstr "Aniqlik Darajasi"

msgid "Engineered for Artists."
msgstr "San'atkorlar uchun Yaratilgan."

msgid "A dual-sided ecosystem designed to elevate the barbering craft to a global standard."
msgstr "Sartaroshlik san'atini global standartga ko'tarish uchun mo'ljallangan ikki tomonlama ekotizim."

msgid "The Client Path"
msgstr "Mijoz Yo'li"

msgid "Discover an elite network of verified master barbers. Book your next masterpiece with 0% friction, manage your style history, and explore trends."
msgstr "Tasdiqlangan usta sartaroshlarning elita tarmog'ini kashf eting. Keyingi asaringizni 0% qiyinchilik bilan band qiling, uslubingiz tarixini boshqaring va trendlarni o'rganing."

msgid "Smart Proximity Discovery"
msgstr "Aqlli Yaqinlikni Aniqlash"

msgid "Adaptive Session Reminders"
msgstr "Moslashuvchan Seans Eslatmalari"

msgid "The Barber Edge"
msgstr "Sartarosh Ustunligi"

msgid "Secure your legacy on a platform built for professionals. High-fidelity video portfolios meet advanced shop analytics and revenue scaling tools."
msgstr "Professionallar uchun yaratilgan platformada o'z merosingizni ta'minlang. Yuqori sifatli video portfellar, ilg'or do'kon tahlillari va daromadni oshirish vositalari bilan birlashadi."

msgid "Master Financial Tracking"
msgstr "Moliyaviy Nazorat"

msgid "Global Portfolio Distribution"
msgstr "Global Portfel Tarqatish"

msgid "Curated Excellence"
msgstr "Tanlangan Mukammallik"

msgid "Tonsor is a closed network. Every professional on this platform is vetted for artistic skill, shop hygiene, and elite client interaction."
msgstr "Tonsor - yopiq tarmoq. Ushbu platformadagi har bir professional badiiy mahorat, do'kon gigienasi va elita mijozlar bilan muloqot bo'yicha tekshiriladi."

msgid "Vetted Professional Network"
msgstr "Tekshirilgan Professional Tarmoq"

msgid "Premium Waitlist Priority"
msgstr "Premium Kutish Ro'yxati Navbati"

msgid "State-of-the-Art"
msgstr "Eng So'nggi Texnologiya"

msgid "Under the hood resides a custom-built infrastructure optimized for speed. 60FPS fluid interactions and precision map discovery come standard."
msgstr "Tizim ostida tezlik uchun optimallashtirilgan maxsus infratuzilma yotadi. 60FPS silliq o'zaro ta'sirlar va aniq xarita kashfiyoti standart hisoblanadi."

msgid "Ultra-Low Latency Booking"
msgstr "O'ta Past Kechikishli Band Qilish"

msgid "Advanced Geospatial Logic"
msgstr "Ilg'or Geofazo Logikasi"

msgid "Choose Your Path."
msgstr "O'z Yo'lingizni Tanlang."

msgid "Define your experience in the Tonsor ecosystem."
msgstr "Tonsor ekotizimida o'z tajribangizni belgilang."

msgid "Client Portal"
msgstr "Mijoz Portali"

msgid "Access the most exclusive barbershops in the network and optimize your grooming schedule."
msgstr "Tarmoqdagi eng eksklyuziv sartaroshxonalarga kiring va parvarishlash jadvalingizni optimallashtiring."

msgid "Enter as Client"
msgstr "Mijoz Sifatida Kirish"

msgid "Barber Portal"
msgstr "Sartarosh Portali"

msgid "Scale your business with professional tools and showcase your identity to elite clientele."
msgstr "O'z biznesingizni professional vositalar bilan kengaytiring va o'zligingizni elita mijozlarga namoyish eting."

msgid "Enter as Barber"
msgstr "Sartarosh Sifatida Kirish"
